General.Name: Gascoyne Resources Ltd
General.Description: Gascoyne Resources Limited engages in the exploration, evaluation, and development of gold projects. Its flagship project is the Dalgaranga gold project, which covers an area of 500 square kilometers located to the northwest of Mount Magnet in the Murchison gold mining region of Western Australia. The company was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in West Perth, Australia.
